title: The Prime Minister and Chief Medical Officer spoke after the National Cabinet meeting this afternoon. This is what we learned
description: Scott Morrison says Australia is entering the "suppression phase" of managing coronavirus. Catch up on his latest update.
content:
Posted 
April 03, 2020 18:48:18
Australia has been eagerly waiting for the result of the latest National Cabinet meeting, held earlier today.
